 Real Madrid and adidas have unveiled the third jersey for the 2020/21 season.
The Spanish champions said the jersey’s design is linked to the roots and traditions of the club.
“With a subtle black and grey design on the front, the jersey is inspired by the paintings on the ceramic tiles that grace the city.
